{"word":"G50 - ἀγνοέω - agnoéō - ag-no-eh'-o - Ignorant","slug":"G50","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀγνοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>agnoéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ag-no-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ignorant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B3;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - agnoeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ag-no-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>; <i>not to know</i> (through lack of information or intelligence); by implication to <i>ignore</i> (through disinclination): - (be) ignorant (-ly), not know, not understand, unknown."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G51\">G51</a>, <a href=\"#/G52\">G52</a>, <a href=\"#/G56\">G56</a>, <a href=\"#/G57\">G57</a>"}]}